### 예상 병목 #3: 매칭 알고리즘 - 동기 순차 처리

**Before (문제 코드)**

```kotlin
fun findBestMatch(requesterId: String, candidates: List<String>): String? {
    val requesterProfile = userProfileRepository.findByUserId(requesterId)
    val requesterPref = preferenceRepository.findByUserId(requesterId)

    return candidates
        .map { candidateId ->
            val profile = userProfileRepository.findByUserId(candidateId) // 순차 DB 조회
            val score = calculateMatchScore(requesterProfile, requesterPref, profile)
            candidateId to score
        }
        .maxByOrNull { it.second }
        ?.first
}
```

50명 후보 × 2회 DB 조회 = 100회 순차 조회.

**After (비동기 병렬 처리 + Redis 프로파일 캐시)**

```kotlin
// UserProfileCacheService.kt
@Service
class UserProfileCacheService(
    private val redisTemplate: RedisTemplate<String, String>,
    private val objectMapper: ObjectMapper,
    private val userProfileRepository: UserProfileRepository
) {
    private val ttl = Duration.ofMinutes(30)

    fun getProfile(userId: String): CachedUserProfile {
        val key = "user:profile:$userId"
        val cached = redisTemplate.opsForValue().get(key)
        if (cached != null) {
            return objectMapper.readValue(cached, CachedUserProfile::class.java)
        }
        // Cache-aside: DB 조회 후 캐시 저장
        val profile = userProfileRepository.findByUserId(userId)
            ?: throw UserNotFoundException(userId)
        val dto = CachedUserProfile.from(profile)
        redisTemplate.opsForValue().set(key, objectMapper.writeValueAsString(dto), ttl)
        return dto
    }

    // 프로파일 변경 시 무효화
    fun evict(userId: String) {
        redisTemplate.delete("user:profile:$userId")
    }
}

// CallMatchingService.kt
@Service
class CallMatchingService(
    private val matchingCacheService: CallMatchingCacheService,
    private val profileCacheService: UserProfileCacheService,
    private val coroutineScope: CoroutineScope  // applicationScope 주입
) {
    suspend fun findBestMatch(requesterId: String): String? {
        val candidates = matchingCacheService.peekCandidates(limit = 50)
        if (candidates.isEmpty()) return null

        val requesterProfile = profileCacheService.getProfile(requesterId)

        // 후보 프로파일 병렬 조회 (Redis 캐시 우선, 모두 비동기)
        val scoredCandidates = candidates
            .filter { it != requesterId }
            .map { candidateId ->
                coroutineScope.async(Dispatchers.IO) {
                    val profile = profileCacheService.getProfile(candidateId)
                    candidateId to calculateMatchScore(requesterProfile, profile)
                }
            }
            .awaitAll()

        return scoredCandidates.maxByOrNull { it.second }?.first
    }

    private fun calculateMatchScore(
        requester: CachedUserProfile,
        candidate: CachedUserProfile
    ): Double {
        var score = 0.0
        if (requester.preferredGender == candidate.gender) score += 40.0
        if (requester.preferredAgeGroup == candidate.ageGroup) score += 30.0
        if (requester.region == candidate.region) score += 20.0
        score += (10.0 - (System.currentTimeMillis() - candidate.queuedAt) / 60000.0).coerceAtLeast(0.0)
        return score
    }
}
```

100회 순차 DB 조회 → Redis 병렬 조회. 예상 응답 시간: 약 200ms → 10ms 이하 (95% 개선).

